Package: rulex
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}
Suggests: ru-tts
Conflicts: ru-tts (<< 1.0)
Description: Russian pronunciation dictionary
 Russian pronunciation dictionary RuLex is aimed primarily for use
 together 		     with the Russian TTS engine Ru_tts. When
 it is installed you can instruct Ru_tts to use the dictionary by the
 command line switch "-s /usr/lib/ru_tts/lexicon".
